      <title>瑞银愿意支付 Greensill 破产所致基金的 90% 利息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/ubs-offers-to-pay-90-on-funds-hit-by-greensill-collapse-video</link>
